zserio.runtime.typeinfo

Class TypeInfo.RecursiveTypeInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • zserio.runtime.typeinfo.TypeInfo.RecursiveTypeInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TypeInfo
    Enclosing interface:
    TypeInfo

    public static final class TypeInfo.RecursiveTypeInfo
extends java.lang.Object
implements TypeInfo
    Type info for recursive types used as a wrapper around generated static typeInfo method to prevent infinite recursion in type info definition.
